        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>For Kicksecure, it is planned to <a href="https://forums.whonix.org/t/replace-sudo-with-doas/17482">replace <code>sudo</code> with <code>doas</code></a> as well as to implement <a href="https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Dev/boot_modes" class="inline-onebox">Role-Based Boot Modes (user versus admin) for Enhanced Security</a>.</p>
          <p><a href="https://forums.kicksecure.com/t/systemd-discussion/766/8">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
