<p>For example, we’re using systemd <a href="https://www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/latest/tmpfiles.d.html">tmpfiles.d</a> / <code>/usr/lib/tmpfiles.d/</code>, while we could implement that some other way. (Which however would make little sense not to do as long as we are using systemd.)</p>
